r\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/VWO\" title=\"Vanguard FTSE Emerging Markets Index Fund ETF Shares\">VWO</a></span>) as an investment option. The fund is managed by Vanguard and its <a href=\"https://investor.vanguard.com/etf/profile/VWO\" rel=\"nofollow\">objective</a> is to \"invest in</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1253986380/image_1253986380.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741988-vwo-emerging-markets-face-a-slew-of-risks-in-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 12:43:48"}, {"id": "4741985", "title": "Hafnia Limited: $100 Million Reason To Hold Your Nose And Stick With The Clean Product Trade", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Stock buyback and Share buybacks is shown using the text\" data-id=\"1912124068\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Andrii Dodonov</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Thesis</h2> <p>In September, I wrote two very bullish pieces on the clean product trade for both TORM plc (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/TRMD\" title=\"TORM plc\">TRMD</a>) and Hafnia Limited (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/HAFN\" title=\"Hafnia Limited\">HAFN</a></span>). <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4723741-hafnia-limited-a-20-percent-yield-and-the-best-value-on-the-water\">The gist of those articles centered around the continued polarization</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1912124068/image_1912124068.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4741985-hafnia-limited-100-million-reason-to-hold-your-nose-and-stick-with-the-clean-product-trade", "pub_date": "2024-12-04 12:33:22"}, {"id": "4741980", "title": "Vertical Aerospace: Rally Is A Good Selling Opportunity", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394967815/image_1394967815.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Conceptual eVTOL (electric vertical take-off and landing) aircrafts as a taxi/shuttle service at the helipad on top of a building\" data-id=\"1394967815\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394967815/image_1394967815.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394967815/image_1394967815.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1394967815/image_1394967815.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://s